title: The new capabilities of Chat GPT 5 - Sydney
abstract: Calum discusses the new and exciting features offered in ChatGPT 5 and explains the impact it will have on the software development industry.
description: Watch Calum's exciting new talk about the features offered by ChatGPT 5, such as contextually aware responses, multi-modal capabilities, and expanded media type support. In his talk he'll in depth about how these features will impact our careers as consultants and change the lives of end users.
